phrases: He said there was some shortcut through Nanatsujiya,
but there is not even anything that looks like a road.
I told that darn Natsume to follow me,
I will wait five seconds for him.
Is not this Natsume's fat cat?
That is a pretty embarrassing name.
You are pretty good for an idiot.
You have not heard about me from Natsume yet?
So, you are a Youkai, Ponta?
I am a very high being.
Do not compare me to those Ayakashi.
This is my first time talking to a Youkai.
That is right, you cannot see us properly.
So, that is why Natsume did not tell you about me?
You would not be much help anyway.
You are not treating him badly, are you?
Any way you look at it, you are more like the follower.
I will not let you say what you want!
Now that you have seen what I really am,
I will have to destroy the evidence!
Why is that cat with you?
He is something like a bodyguard.
if you do not want to talk about it, it is okay.
It is pretty complex, so I am not sure how to explain it all.
Ah, well, it is not like I wanted to hide it from you.
I wanted to talk with you normally.
That is why I did not want to put you through anything miserable.
Are you in a miserable situation?
All right, let us go take a look, Natsume.
They are still setting it up.
I do not care, let us go!
The temple is on my way home, so I will tag along.
Oh, it is not open yet?
I told you they were still setting up.
I thought the street stands might have been open already.
They are here, are not they?
I heard they gather where it is really lively.
There are a lot of them.
I am right, are not I?
Sorry, but could you take this to the front of the shrine?
Please take that to the shrine.
Hurry up, I am in the middle of a conversation.
Do not talk back to the class rep.
We are in difference classes though.
I am sure Natsume will come to the festival.
You did it now, you rascally fox!
I will not let you go!
Are not you being a bit too rough?
This has nothing to do with you!
Did you see the fox do it?
But he is the only one around here!
Looks like it was the wind.
It is so empty here that it is almost surprising, huh?
Look at the corner of the ceiling.
There is not a pond in the backyard.
So, I think only we can see the water reflection on the ceiling.
So, Tanuma cannot see the pond.
If he is here, then Natsume will come back.
Excuse me, do you have any rope?
Oh, and as tough as possible.
No, Natsume, those are not my whiskers.
Did you come to meet him?
I am sure he will come.
I see, I hope you will meet him.
Takashi-kun could have told us he would be going straight to the festival.
But, if he is in an accident...
Nyangoro will come tell us if that happens.
How long has it been since Takashi came here?
I am sure he is gone through a lot of tough things,
But with him going out on his own like this, puts me at ease.
Being too considerate of each other is not being a family.
We were a bit too early.
All right, I will hold on to it.
All right, I will save you!
Could you help me for a bit?
How about we split up and look?
I do not see your pouch.
You cannot remember where you dropped it?
Is what is inside so important?
No, did you see my cat?
I just gave it to you.
I am not going to pay for what I did not get!
It is medicine that allows me to be human for a while.
I will because Natsume trouble if I am in my animal form.
I see, so that is how it is.
All right, I will go and...
You came here because of the smell of food, did not you, little fox?
I will let it go in the mountains then.
That is strange, I am sure I lowered the fire.
It is dangerous if you are in a crowd of people with that form.
If you are here, Hiiragi, then Natori-san is here too?
He asked you to watch her?
You are being careless talking to me in such a crowded area.
Are you that little fox from before?
Damn that Natsume, he did not even come to save me.
You could see the pond in my backyard, right?
All I can see are the shadows on the ceiling.
Does Touko-san know you can see these things?
You do not believe in them?
They are kind, so I am sure they will believe me if I tell them.
I am sure they will feel bad because they have cared for me so much.
but I do not like it.
I want them to always be smiling.
It is better than I thought.
I thought it would have been more shabby since it is the countryside.
Sorry, I actually cannot see it.
There is some big guy in the way.
I can tell that it is pretty though.
He is gazing at it so intently.
Let us walk for a bit.
There might be some place so you can see too.
I can see it well here.
What color are the shadow fish?
So, this is where you are, you heartless bastard.
I cannot believe you left your precious bodyguard, you...!
I could hear the winter's footsteps approaching.
